1
00:00:00,531 --> 00:00:05,055
♪A little bit sorry for my love for you♪

2
00:00:05,055 --> 00:00:10,559
♪Sorry, I was a little late♪

3
00:00:10,559 --> 00:00:16,987
♪I really want the unconscious longing
to appear faster♪

4
00:00:16,987 --> 00:00:21,467
♪Can I get closer
and hear you say "I do" once more♪

5
00:00:21,467 --> 00:00:25,915
♪Holding hands, the scenery
in midsummer is a new journey♪

6
00:00:25,915 --> 00:00:30,826
♪The chapters of a fairy tale
are performed one after another♪

7
00:00:30,826 --> 00:00:34,875
♪The promised moment
will definitely not be forgotten♪

8
00:00:34,875 --> 00:00:39,410
♪Can I get closer and listen to
the frequency of your heartbeat♪

9
00:00:39,410 --> 00:00:43,707
♪Start the countdown 4321,
a new scenery♪

10
00:00:43,707 --> 00:00:48,472
♪I want to see all the scenes about you♪

11
00:00:48,472 --> 00:00:51,963
♪No need to miss you anymore♪

12
00:00:51,963 --> 00:00:55,643
♪Right by your side♪

13
00:00:57,289 --> 00:01:00,667
=Jin Secretary=

14
00:01:00,667 --> 00:01:03,008
=Episode 1=

15
00:01:33,566 --> 00:01:36,699
Do you accept Gu Qianqian
as your lawful wife,

16
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:40,300
loving and caring for her
for a lifetime,

17
00:01:40,533 --> 00:01:41,800
till death do you part?

18
00:01:44,600 --> 00:01:45,566
I object.

19
00:01:46,112 --> 00:01:50,304
♪Stars fall into my eyes,
and you fall into my heart♪

20
00:01:50,304 --> 00:01:54,498
♪I make a wish foolishly,
but actually, you are the shooting star♪

21
00:01:54,498 --> 00:01:56,213
♪Open my secret♪

22
00:01:57,566 --> 00:01:58,500
I object.

23
00:01:58,500 --> 00:02:00,500
(I am Jin Xi'er.)

24
00:02:00,500 --> 00:02:04,666
(I can't believe I'm trying)

25
00:02:04,666 --> 00:02:09,099
(to steal a man away from a wedding.)

26
00:02:09,100 --> 00:02:11,966
(It's all for that narcissistic guy.)

27
00:02:13,533 --> 00:02:14,800
(A year ago,)

28
00:02:15,233 --> 00:02:17,633
(I got the golden belt
for free sparring overseas.)

29
00:02:18,720 --> 00:02:19,904
(Twin elder sister Jin Xi'er)

30
00:02:20,566 --> 00:02:22,333
(Unexpectedly, my younger sister)

31
00:02:23,100 --> 00:02:25,000
(was bullied in the workplace.)

32
00:02:25,366 --> 00:02:26,966
(I had to rush back urgently.)

33
00:02:30,272 --> 00:02:31,645
(Twin younger sister Jin Xi'en)

34
00:02:33,920 --> 00:02:38,368
(Bili Country, Horton City)

35
00:02:38,633 --> 00:02:40,933
(This company bullied my sister.)

36
00:02:41,166 --> 00:02:42,700
(I'll teach you a lesson.)

37
00:02:49,504 --> 00:02:51,936
(WE Beauty Family)

38
00:02:55,566 --> 00:02:56,366
Dork Jin.

39
00:02:58,133 --> 00:03:02,000
It's been a month.
You finally came back to work.

40
00:03:02,233 --> 00:03:04,800
(She didn't recognize me, as expected.)

41
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:05,933
What did you say?

42
00:03:09,900 --> 00:03:13,733
You're just a secretary
trying to please the president.

43
00:03:14,766 --> 00:03:17,566
Hello, WE Beauty Family.

44
00:03:19,266 --> 00:03:19,933
Hey.

45
00:03:19,933 --> 00:03:21,200
What's wrong with you?

46
00:03:24,533 --> 00:03:26,133
Where is Liang Liangqiang?

47
00:03:32,700 --> 00:03:36,400
(Strange. She seems like
a different person with a great strength.)

48
00:03:37,900 --> 00:03:39,233
Miss Jin?

49
00:03:41,833 --> 00:03:44,466
You make me mad. Are you a fool?

50
00:03:44,533 --> 00:03:46,233
You can't even make coffee?

51
00:03:47,700 --> 00:03:52,000
You can't even make coffee. Stupid.
No wonder you can't afford luxury stuff.

52
00:03:54,566 --> 00:03:56,833
You're so useless.

53
00:03:58,633 --> 00:03:59,966
Who let you in?

54
00:04:02,933 --> 00:04:07,133
You need others to make you coffee.
Do you also need help with your work?

55
00:04:07,133 --> 00:04:08,600
Dork Jin, what are you doing?

56
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:12,800
What do you want?

57
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:15,233
I was wrong.

58
00:04:15,233 --> 00:04:17,466
I'm sorry. I made a mistake.

59
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:20,033
I will do my work on my own.

60
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:23,400
You sissy.

61
00:04:25,733 --> 00:04:29,899
No matter how long you work overtime,

62
00:04:29,900 --> 00:04:31,233
just get it done for me.

63
00:04:33,300 --> 00:04:35,133
Are you a fool?

64
00:04:35,133 --> 00:04:36,899
Can you do it quickly?

65
00:04:36,900 --> 00:04:38,700
Be efficient, alright?

66
00:04:38,700 --> 00:04:41,000
Don't make me urge you.

67
00:04:41,333 --> 00:04:42,133
Useless.

68
00:04:50,624 --> 00:04:52,900
Ouch, you don't need to work overtime.

69
00:04:52,900 --> 00:04:54,233
Everyone doesn't, either.

70
00:04:54,233 --> 00:04:55,899
I won't force them.

71
00:04:55,900 --> 00:04:57,300
What are you looking at?

72
00:04:57,300 --> 00:04:59,233
Focus on your work.

73
00:04:59,233 --> 00:05:00,299
No goofing off.

74
00:05:00,366 --> 00:05:02,399
What did you do?

75
00:05:02,399 --> 00:05:06,199
How can you be so brainless? How?

76
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:08,866
Redo it for me. Right now.

77
00:05:13,700 --> 00:05:16,700
You have been exploiting my sister.

78
00:05:21,833 --> 00:05:22,666
What are you doing?

79
00:05:26,200 --> 00:05:27,800
I won't shift the blame to others.

80
00:05:28,033 --> 00:05:29,233
What's wrong with Miss Jin?

81
00:05:29,233 --> 00:05:30,766
What happened? She can fight?

82
00:05:30,766 --> 00:05:32,766
She hit people. Call security.

83
00:05:33,166 --> 00:05:34,699
What's going on?

84
00:05:36,700 --> 00:05:37,866
Mr. Li.

85
00:05:37,866 --> 00:05:39,699
Alright, calm down.

86
00:05:39,700 --> 00:05:41,666
We'll solve any issues later.

87
00:05:42,133 --> 00:05:44,733
Now there's an emergency.
Miss Jin, come with me.

88
00:05:47,033 --> 00:05:50,633
Miss Jin, come on.
There's a big problem with Mr. Lan.

89
00:05:52,466 --> 00:05:54,866
Do you know how much we lost this time?

90
00:05:55,533 --> 00:05:56,433
Check out the report yourself.

91
00:05:57,433 --> 00:05:59,266
If I hadn't found out in time,

92
00:05:59,266 --> 00:06:00,933
we would have lost more.

93
00:06:02,466 --> 00:06:07,433
(Alright, let me teach a lesson
to their boss.)

94
00:06:09,533 --> 00:06:10,599
(News from abroad.)

95
00:06:10,600 --> 00:06:15,100
(Elite Lan Chen won World Financial Elite Award)
(Mr. Lan Chen won World Financial Elite Award.)

96
00:06:15,100 --> 00:06:15,500
(He returns home today.)

97
00:06:15,500 --> 00:06:17,100
(Due to his father's early death,)

98
00:06:17,100 --> 00:06:19,866
(his grandfather has been seeing him
as the heir to the family business.)

99
00:06:19,866 --> 00:06:23,666
(Now he is the youngest president
in the history of WE Beauty Family.)

100
00:06:23,666 --> 00:06:25,066
(His grandfather is living abroad.)

101
00:06:25,066 --> 00:06:26,366
(Lan Chen's future is promising.)

102
00:06:26,366 --> 00:06:27,533
(And he is unmarried.)

103
00:06:27,533 --> 00:06:30,766
(His mother has been working
on a business marriage with Gu Group.)

104
00:06:30,766 --> 00:06:34,233
Mr. Lan, I heard
that WE Group had financial problems.

105
00:06:34,233 --> 00:06:36,099
Do you need Lihuai's investment badly?

106
00:06:37,266 --> 00:06:40,133
Are you already engaged to Gu Qianqian?

107
00:06:40,733 --> 00:06:41,933
What is your relationship?

108
00:06:45,033 --> 00:06:48,266
Mr. Lan, I heard
that WE Group had financial problems.

109
00:06:48,266 --> 00:06:50,299
Someone leaked the news
of Mr. Lan's return.

110
00:06:50,300 --> 00:06:52,300
Reporters have been following him.

111
00:06:52,300 --> 00:06:54,304
Reporters? I can't be violent then.

112
00:06:56,033 --> 00:06:58,080
Miss Jin, we can't hit reporters.

113
00:07:04,166 --> 00:07:07,033
He is not Mr. Lan.

114
00:07:07,033 --> 00:07:08,333
What's going on?

115
00:07:08,333 --> 00:07:10,533
Where is Lan Chen?

116
00:07:19,700 --> 00:07:22,000
Mr. Lan, welcome back.

117
00:07:23,533 --> 00:07:25,299
2 minutes 15 seconds.

118
00:07:25,300 --> 00:07:28,633
(Hubus Elite in China Under 30, Lan Chen)

119
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:34,100
Do you know
how much I can do within that time?

120
00:07:35,433 --> 00:07:36,766
You're too slow.

121
00:07:38,033 --> 00:07:40,433
Is this your efficiency
in handling emergencies?

122
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:43,633
Without a stand-in today,

123
00:07:43,733 --> 00:07:45,400
much more time would have been wasted.

124
00:07:46,366 --> 00:07:48,700
Sorry, Mr. Lan. We'll do it better...

125
00:07:48,700 --> 00:07:49,333
And,

126
00:07:50,266 --> 00:07:51,066
look,

127
00:07:51,200 --> 00:07:53,566
your expression is terrible.

128
00:08:03,333 --> 00:08:06,299
I don't allow my secretary
to make such a stupid mistake.

129
00:08:10,900 --> 00:08:12,500
Work on your expression.

130
00:08:12,500 --> 00:08:14,016
Otherwise, I'll fire you.

131
00:08:21,971 --> 00:08:26,493
♪I pass through the crowd with you♪

132
00:08:29,523 --> 00:08:34,484
♪As if we have a tacit understanding,
attracting each other♪

133
00:08:37,533 --> 00:08:43,357
♪When the loneliness cracks,
warmth seeps in♪

134
00:08:43,357 --> 00:08:49,792
♪You come with light,
shining into my heart♪

135
00:08:50,827 --> 00:08:54,308
♪Stars fall into my eyes,
and you fall into my heart♪

136
00:08:54,308 --> 00:08:58,429
♪I make a wish foolishly,
but actually, you are the shooting star♪

137
00:08:58,429 --> 00:09:00,125
♪Open my secret♪

138
00:09:00,125 --> 00:09:06,173
♪I hope you find
all the tenderness hidden for you♪

139
00:09:06,173 --> 00:09:10,045
♪Sinking into your love,
I want to sink deeper♪

140
00:09:10,045 --> 00:09:14,551
♪With each breath,
I can feel the sweetness♪

141
00:09:16,512 --> 00:09:23,261
♪Two lonely islands meet,
and it's the gift of fate♪
